    <node id="Маленький принц">
      <data key="d0">Маленький принц</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Маленький принц is described as an unnamed prince who lived on a planet full of plants and creatures. He had the ability to understand the significance of small seeds that could become huge baobabs, which he considered important for life's beauty and fragility. The prince was curious about his surroundings, including the giant baobabs, and attempted to share his insights with others through drawings. Additionally, he warned about the potential dangers associated with these massive trees. He is also depicted as a human character in Antoine de Saint-Exupéry’s novella "Le Petit Prince".&lt;SEP&gt;A young prince character in the story "The Little Prince"</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-265544bb40b451cd313707a2a4b33ff4-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-6b2ba88f29d6d77fed85771bc5dc9981-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-adc6c168dbb425d9ece24d5bc28b2fcc-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7ff80b28ae61d87cbbd16fc2977b0881-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a4e544d8de8adf2c2d92737023d20063-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-483c61454a03ee080cf5d72363c83c1b-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
