    <edge source="Маленький принц" target="Троех кустов">
      <data key="d7">3.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The prince mistakenly thought the three bushes were a kind of baobab, indicating that he did not realize their true nature and potential danger.&lt;SEP&gt;The prince mentioned these bushes to warn others about the dangers they might pose if not managed properly.&lt;SEP&gt;The prince warned others about the potential dangers these bushes might pose if not managed properly.</data>
      <data key="d9">caution,eats</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782408993</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
