      <data key="d7">2.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Explained how to show love for a colorful flower&lt;SEP&gt;Discussed the reason for having spines</data>
      <data key="d9">explained_how_to_show_love_for_a_colorful_flower,talked_about_the_reason_for_having_spines</data>
